name: Descent - Manusia & Wajah
description: 'MANUSIA' is a Malay term meaning human, a direct references to the writer and all of the variants before him. 'WAJAH' is a term in Malay meaning face, referring to the multiple faces of the Unseeing, that goes with the nature of the Unseeing being manipulative and wearing many faces to deceive the humans and other entities. The dead spacemen floating and surrounding the Unseeing were the slave of the false deity's lies.
